== MxmlCleaner
Be sure to have a back up of your files before you execute the clean.
This script comes with no warranty, and the author will not be held liable for problems caused by executing the script.

To run the cleaner do the following:
1. cd to the lib folder
2. ruby main.rb ${the_path_to_a_folder_that_contains_mxml_files}
eg:
ruby main.rb C:\dev\my-project\src\main\flex


